            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Author's comment. The measurements of the cumulative",
                "decay of the Nd-141 ground state do not provide the",
                "total (n,2n) reaction cross section exactly because",
                "of the interference caused by the decay of the",
                "metastable state.The measurement provides",
                "sig-g + 1.007 sig-m for the Nd-142(n,2n) reaction,",
                "which is given in the data column."
